            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Given a PR opened by the Junior Dev agent, write dedicated tests, run them, and on failure hand work back to the Junior agent.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "attrs": {
              "level": 2
            },
            "content": [
