            ],
            "type": "heading"
          },
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Create the Junior Developer agent: a headless Claude Code session that picks up a ticket flagged \"easy\" by the Development Orchestrator, plans and implements the change, pushes a branch, and opens a PR.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "Three files to create:",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "text": "- ",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
